Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:06.06,標題,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)\pos(796,249)}活动室 DE 补习
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.49,0:00:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人 加油的说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凸守永远与主人同在的说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟游同学之前的小考成绩实在太差了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.59,0:00:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底考了几分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,22分…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不及格了啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}勇太好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.37,0:00:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花的英语不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.15,0:00:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在小考的前一天受到了魔术师协会的袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.94,0:00:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,负了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.07,0:00:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 那这道题你也会做的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体受到了联合王国教的邪恶意念攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:49.24,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(612,660)}<United Kingdom>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.41,0:00:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主…主人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凸守…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.02,0:00:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.59,0:00:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:00:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:01:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然是联合王国教 那他们是说英语的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:01:00.38,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(486,660)}<United Kingdom>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hallo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.63,0:01:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hallo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.94,0:01:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}By the way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.94,0:01:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顺便一提
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}What do you do on the weekend usually
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你周末一般会做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}I like cooking and reading books
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢料理和阅读
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}So I always do on my day off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我经常这样度过假日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.39,0:01:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}Do you wanna join?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.39,0:01:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意跟我一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.24,0:01:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…说日语就OK
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那做题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.13,0:01:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强烈的即视感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.04,0:01:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟游同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.39,0:01:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你平时不是经常念那些类似英语、德语的咒语吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.09,0:01:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德语很帅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很帅的说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.98,0:01:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汉字也很帅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.88,0:01:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如「暗」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「斩」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.27,0:01:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「污秽」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.28,0:01:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「断罪」之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,富㭴喜欢汉字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 这不是中二病一类的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是生于日本的喜悦…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:02:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是对中国四千年历史的尊重…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是漆黑烈焰使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:02.24,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(698,660)}<Dark Flame Master>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到暗炎龙恩泽之人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你难道听不出我在拼命否认吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是邪王真眼同时也是漆黑堕天使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以还是说英语、德语比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.81,0:02:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么感觉龙套指数飙升了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 小鸟游同学的折伞也有个奇怪的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.59,0:02:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是折伞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是 灾厄之六 完美定制GelZone UNSAS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:30.43,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(690,660)}<Schwarz Sechs Perfect Customize GelZone UNSAS>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.57,0:02:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都叫你别把GelZone UNSAS加进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它是攻防兼备的划时代人工制品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.10,0:02:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此能同时成为最强之矛与最强之盾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顺便一提 还能防雨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那还不是伞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那请你解释一下刚才的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schwarz Sechs Perfect Customize GelZone UNSAS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英语翻成日语 日语翻成英语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:02:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小七… 恶鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是折伞…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么Schwarz Sechs Perfect Customize GelZone UNSAS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用日语该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.60,0:03:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这是你取的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天上天下唯我独尊的某种机械的改良版
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就… 就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是非常厉害的武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太… 怎么办啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都忘了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的脑袋是鸡脑袋吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.58,註釋,,0000,0000,0000,,日本有个说法，鸡走三步就忘事。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咯咯咯！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太 世界在晃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正确答案是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漆黑六号 完美定制版
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GelZone UNSAS是什么来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个请忘记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好帅！
